        <simpara>The typical maximum storage time in the refrigerator is:</simpara>

        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <simpara>
                    <emphasis>1 Weeks</emphasis> in the fridge, if stored there immediately after purchase, whether sealed or not
                </simpara>
            </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>

        <simpara>(The above applies to: 'Meat: Smoked or Processed: Ham (Fresh, cook-before-eating, Shoulder Roll (Butt), boneless)'.)</simpara>

